if possible get the cobalt bp and legs and if you are ogre get bracer to. this assumes that you are able to afford it. if you have those 3 items in cobalt and the other items in thurg armor you will be well rounded and be pretty well prepared for a lot of situations. then just get a pegusus cloak so you can lev self and you are a boyscout with all your utility functions =)<br>
